1
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:35,030
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:39,370
[2005]

3
00:01:41,229 --> 00:01:43,400
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

4
00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:45,600
Xiaolan,

5
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:46,509
you rarely

6
00:01:46,509 --> 00:01:47,229
hang out with us.

7
00:01:47,229 --> 00:01:48,759
We've never heard you sing.

8
00:01:48,789 --> 00:01:51,310
I-I'm a terrible singer.

9
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,000
I think I'll pass.

10
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:55,390
What song would you like to hear?

11
00:02:07,250 --> 00:02:10,300
[Episode 20 The Most Romantic Thing]

12
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:16,079
[Spring, 1991]

13
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:23,070
[Mr. Chen Xiliang, Ms. Teresa Li]

14
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:28,470
Congratulations.

15
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,680
Hope you're the next one to get married.

16
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,310
Zhenzhu,

17
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:33,710
you look stunning today.

18
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,000
Hello, uncles, aunties.

19
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,060
Hello, Auntie Liu.

20
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,440
Sis Bai.

21
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,400
Do I look good?

22
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,680
Yes, terrific.

23
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,240
Listen,

24
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:44,150
now you're a mix

25
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:46,370
of heroism and charm,

26
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,150
efficiency and gentleness.

27
00:02:48,910 --> 00:02:49,360
Okay.

28
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:50,630
Nice compliments.

29
00:02:50,630 --> 00:02:51,630
I won't change my clothes to go

30
00:02:51,630 --> 00:02:52,410
pick up the goods later.

31
00:02:52,410 --> 00:02:53,400
You'll handle all the work.

32
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:53,960
No problem.

33
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,870
To help you stay pretty,

34
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:56,380
I'll do my part of the job and yours.

35
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:57,840
You're such a bootlicker.

36
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,240
Auntie Liu,

37
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:00,870
the wedding's about to start.

38
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:02,310
Why isn't Xiaolan here yet?

39
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:03,590
Xiaolan told me to come without her

40
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:04,400
since she had something to do.

41
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,730
She should arrive soon.

42
00:03:08,430 --> 00:03:10,960
Magpies in the sky
are chirping with delight.

43
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:13,220
A couple on earth is to be wedded tonight.

44
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,530
Everyone, thank you

45
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,470
for attending

46
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,079
the grand wedding ceremony

47
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:19,210
for Mr. Chen Xiliang and Ms. Teresa Li.

48
00:03:19,250 --> 00:03:21,160
Here, on behalf of the newlyweds,

49
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:22,100
I'd like to extend

50
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:23,940
a warm welcome to all of you!

51
00:03:23,970 --> 00:03:24,840
Welcome!

52
00:03:28,390 --> 00:03:28,920
Now,

53
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,800
let's give a big round

54
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:32,150
of applause

55
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:33,280
to this happy couple

56
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:36,079
as they make their glamorous entrance!

57
00:03:54,810 --> 00:03:55,410
Come here!

58
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:56,680
Hurry, Xiaolan.

59
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,000
It just began.

60
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,360
Okay.

61
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:09,710
They are such a perfect match

62
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,870
made for each other.

63
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:12,030
Won't you say so?

64
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,430
-Yes!
-Yes!

65
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,190
The groom is such

66
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:18,010
a handsome man with an elegant bearing.

67
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,600
Guys,

68
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:19,920
isn't he charming?

69
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,120
-Yes!
-Very much so!

70
00:04:21,190 --> 00:04:22,160
The bride

71
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,890
is breathtakingly beautiful.

72
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,650
Guys,

73
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,800
isn't she pretty?

74
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,240
-Yes!
-So pretty!

75
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:28,800
Next,

76
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:30,270
let's move on to the first part

77
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:30,950
of the wedding.

78
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:32,110
What took you two so long?

79
00:04:32,110 --> 00:04:33,950
We were preparing a gift for Chen Xiliang.

80
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:35,000
It cost us some time.

81
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:35,720
What gift?

82
00:04:36,930 --> 00:04:37,730
It's a secret.

83
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:45,120
-Bite it!
-Go for it!

84
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,000
-Try again!
-Once again!

85
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,600
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

86
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:55,820
Do it again!

87
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:00,910
Is it done now?

88
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:02,070
All done!

89
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:02,960
Bravo!

90
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,120
Come on, Sis Bai, Auntie Liu.

91
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,000
H-Have some pork.

92
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,830
Auntie Liu, try the roast suckling pig.

93
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:09,030
Get me some more meat.

94
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:11,390
We'd like to raise a toast to you all.

95
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:12,720
Here is the bride and groom.

96
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,070
Congrats on your wedding!

97
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:14,630
Congrats!

98
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:16,290
Thanks. Thank you, everyone.

99
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:22,430
Xia.

100
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:24,110
This toast...

101
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,320
is especially to you.

102
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:27,050
Without you

103
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:27,680
or Luna,

104
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:28,630
Teresa and I

105
00:05:28,630 --> 00:05:30,430
wouldn't have gotten together.

106
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:31,480
Xiaolan,

107
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,510
thank you for recommending

108
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:33,950
I shoot the commercial back then.

109
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,350
I'm very grateful to you.

110
00:05:35,630 --> 00:05:36,680
Chen, Teresa,

111
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:37,950
even without me,

112
00:05:37,970 --> 00:05:39,040
Luna would've been established

113
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,680
and you would've become a happy couple
as you are today.

114
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,190
You created all that yourselves.

115
00:05:42,190 --> 00:05:42,650
Cheers.

116
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:43,409
Cheers.

117
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,480
Thanks to you all.

118
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,540
Congratulations!

119
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,690
Thank you so much...

120
00:05:47,050 --> 00:05:48,159
for taking time out to be with us.

121
00:05:48,159 --> 00:05:48,920
Many thanks.

122
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:49,870
Goodbye.

123
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:50,600
Take care.

124
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,450
I won't see you off then!

125
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,720
Chen.

126
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:56,520
You're leaving too?

127
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,600
No, we're not.

128
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,980
A wedding gift for you.

129
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,000
Car keys?

130
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,610
What do you mean?

131
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,750
The car is not just for you,

132
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:07,880
but for Luna as well.

133
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,240
You'll need a car for meeting clients

134
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:09,830
and whatever

135
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,230
in the future, won't you?

136
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:13,600
This is too big a gift.

137
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,560
I can't take it.

138
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:15,360
Just keep it.

139
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:15,990
It's fine.

140
00:06:15,990 --> 00:06:17,320
There's one more thing.

141
00:06:18,580 --> 00:06:19,870
Please read the agreement.

142
00:06:19,870 --> 00:06:21,750
I'm afraid Xiaolan will be too busy
to involve herself

143
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:23,310
in Luna's business from now on.

144
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:23,950
So...

145
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:27,370
[Equity Transfer Agreement]

146
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:39,790
♪ The stars flow across the sky,
and I walk this road with you ♪

147
00:06:32,870 --> 00:06:33,480
Xia,

148
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,040
Luna was built up

149
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,900
by us together.

150
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:37,070
Why don't we sit down and talk about

151
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:37,930
this decision?

152
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:38,970
-I think…
-Chen,

153
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,360
didn't we already make a pact

154
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,510
in the very beginning?

155
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:44,540
♪ From strangers,
our hearts slowly grow close ♪

156
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:48,060
♪ Quietly, we treat each other
with sincerity ♪

157
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:45,820
Yes, we did.

158
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:47,570
You said from the start

159
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,560
that selling clothes wasn't your dream.

160
00:06:49,030 --> 00:06:56,950
♪ Life is like a dream,
and friends are like a mist ♪

161
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:53,170
How about this?

162
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:54,230
If you ever

163
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,800
need my help in the future,

164
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,730
just let me know.

165
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,159
Don't stand on ceremony at all.

166
00:06:58,100 --> 00:07:01,890
♪ True confidants are rare,
after storms and trials ♪

167
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,730
I, Chen Xiliang,

168
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,000
might not have great capability,

169
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,860
but I'll always

170
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:09,010
♪ The one who never steps back for me,
that is you ♪

171
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,790
do whatever I can to help you.

172
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:08,140
When your residential buildings
are finished,

173
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:09,750
I'll definitely buy an apartment.

174
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:13,680
♪ In the distant night sky,
the scattered stars are all connected ♪

175
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:10,600
Okay.

176
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,750
Congrats on the wedding, Chen.

177
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:13,350
Thank you.

178
00:07:13,710 --> 00:07:19,210
♪ Even if the road ahead
is full of thorns ♪

179
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,360
Xiliang!

180
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:17,360
Coming!

181
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:18,680
I need to go now.

182
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,070
Sure.

183
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:19,770
Go ahead.

184
00:07:20,050 --> 00:07:23,180
♪ You help untangle
the loneliness in my heart ♪

185
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,220
I'll keep this.

186
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,210
Here I come!

187
00:07:23,210 --> 00:07:26,770
♪ Who truly understands me? ♪

188
00:07:27,170 --> 00:07:31,080
♪ Like two hands,
together in joy and in sorrow ♪

189
00:07:31,110 --> 00:07:36,790
♪ We share everything,
never dividing between you and me ♪

190
00:07:37,580 --> 00:07:41,710
♪ You for me, and I for you ♪

191
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:42,470
What's wrong, honey?

192
00:07:42,530 --> 00:07:48,680
♪ Facing hardship and despair together,
tightly holding your hand ♪

193
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:48,409
Listen,

194
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:50,360
you don't want to waste your time on them.

195
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:50,920
Let's go.

196
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,320
Pardon me.

197
00:07:52,870 --> 00:07:54,730
You don't sound like a gentleman.

198
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:57,750
It looks like this lady
has something to say.

199
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,430
Okay.

200
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:00,800
Then you guys talk.

201
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,330
I'll wait for you upstairs.

202
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:05,600
What now?

203
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,800
Are you here to laugh at me?

204
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:10,040
Ji Ya,

205
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,240
don't you think you're a bit

206
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,390
too full of yourself?

207
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:14,510
I don't know what you're talking about.

208
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:15,360
Xia, Zhou Cheng!

209
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,510
I knew you would still be around.

210
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,720
I just ran into
some garment factory staff.

211
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,320
They told me Ji Ya's brand...

212
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,240
Because its rapid expansion outpaced

213
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,000
sales growth,

214
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,190
its American investor
wouldn't inject more capital.

215
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:28,050
The brand has been auctioned off.

216
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,510
You're here too?

217
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:31,390
Hello, Ms. Ji.

218
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,549
Goodbye, Ms. Ji.

219
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:34,799
Oh, right!

220
00:08:35,030 --> 00:08:35,730
Come have a drink

221
00:08:35,730 --> 00:08:36,860
on the second floor.

222
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,330
Xia Xiaolan,

223
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,130
you've gone way out of line.

224
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,090
To be honest,

225
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,510
I'm very pleased

226
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:46,630
to hear about the failure

227
00:08:46,630 --> 00:08:48,550
of a rival of mine
who once tried to destroy me

228
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:49,680
with devious means.

229
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:50,790
That said,

230
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,460
I also feel sorry about it.

231
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:53,390
Ji Ya,

232
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:54,480
you are

233
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,880
an excellent designer.

234
00:08:56,260 --> 00:08:56,790
Elegance

235
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:58,770
could have developed much better.

236
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:00,960
Elegance's positioning

237
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:03,320
was actually much higher-end than Luna's.

238
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,200
In fact, we didn't have to

239
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,870
go for a cut-throat competition.

240
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:07,790
But you got willy-nilly with your actions,

241
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:08,600
since you arrogantly

242
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,960
thought there would always be

243
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,290
someone to bail you out.

244
00:09:11,950 --> 00:09:12,760
Ms. Ji,

245
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,120
the world isn't that simple.

246
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,270
Is that so?

247
00:09:17,470 --> 00:09:18,870
Thank you for the advice.

248
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:27,440
Ji Ya doesn't seem to care

249
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,720
a lot about her brand.

250
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:31,510
Although I did foresee

251
00:09:31,510 --> 00:09:33,000
that Ji Ya's reckless expansion

252
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,330
would lead to problems,

253
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,150
I didn't expect

254
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:36,810
her brand to collapse so soon.

255
00:09:37,910 --> 00:09:39,000
From what Chen said,

256
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,750
it was that American man

257
00:09:39,750 --> 00:09:41,480
who refused to pour more money into it.

258
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,030
He initially

259
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:44,360
invested in the brand
just to pursue Ji Ya.

260
00:09:44,630 --> 00:09:45,960
He is a businessman after all.

261
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,240
He wouldn't keep throwing money

262
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,500
into a bottomless pit.

263
00:09:48,910 --> 00:09:50,710
They've gone for afternoon tea.

264
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,500
Do you think they'll enjoy it?

265
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:55,030
I hope he's a faithful romantic partner.

266
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,750
Otherwise, Ms. Ji Ya

267
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:58,350
might stir up trouble again.

268
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:07,200
This is my lucky place.

269
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:07,910
I'm especially happy

270
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:09,040
every time I am here.

271
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:13,920
Xiaolan!

272
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:14,760
Uncle.

273
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:15,360
Ms. Xia.

274
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:16,530
Come on.

275
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,480
Quickly,

276
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:21,000
tell us

277
00:10:21,030 --> 00:10:22,570
about the hotel.

278
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:25,080
Haihua Hotel is the first
five-star international hotel

279
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,270
in Shengcheng.

280
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:27,870
Its shareholders are

281
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:29,600
Meihua, Huifeng Bank,

282
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:30,630
the Merchants Group,

283
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:31,960
and Dongfeng Holdings.

284
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:33,550
They are all from Gangdao,

285
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:35,150
except Dongfeng,
the only mainland enterprise.

286
00:10:35,150 --> 00:10:35,600
Yes.

287
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,750
Meihua and Dongfeng Holdings

288
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:39,870
are competing
for the hotel's management rights.

289
00:10:39,870 --> 00:10:40,930
Meihua's proposal

290
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:42,360
was vetoed by Dongfeng,

291
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:43,840
while Dongfeng's plan

292
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,470
was disproved by the three shareholders

293
00:10:45,470 --> 00:10:46,270
from Gangdao.

294
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,510
So, now, Dongfeng is looking

295
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:48,740
to revise their proposal,

296
00:10:48,740 --> 00:10:50,510
which gives us Yuanhui an opportunity.

297
00:10:50,510 --> 00:10:51,320
That is to say,

298
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:54,120
it's not only a competition on designs,

299
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:56,170
but also a battle for control.

300
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,440
An executive of Dongfeng

301
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,440
is in Shengcheng.

302
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,660
His surname is Huo.

303
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:03,530
He is the one we are meeting today.

304
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,750
Yuanhui isn't the only company
eager for cooperation.

305
00:11:05,750 --> 00:11:06,910
There's a fierce competition,

306
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:08,360
but also a good chance to shine.

307
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,240
Today, let's first figure out

308
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,510
what they want exactly.

309
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:11,360
Okay, got it.

310
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:11,960
Let's go.

311
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:12,320
Go.

312
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,270
We will follow this lead

313
00:11:20,270 --> 00:11:21,070
to dig deeper.

314
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,320
As far as we know,

315
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,960
the crane operators
on the construction site

316
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,000
are loosely managed

317
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,460
and replaced frequently.

318
00:11:26,670 --> 00:11:28,240
It's hard to find a particular someone.

319
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,170
But don't worry.

320
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,080
We will make sure

321
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,080
you get an answer.

322
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:32,390
I know.

323
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:33,550
I won't give up

324
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:34,680
on this case either.

325
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:35,790
We'll keep you posted

326
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:36,790
on any new developments.

327
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:37,200
Okay.

328
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:40,150
It's actually fine for us
to notify your law firm

329
00:11:40,150 --> 00:11:41,480
when anything comes up.

330
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,480
It must be tough being attorneys like you.

331
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,870
You shouldn't keep running back and forth.

332
00:11:44,870 --> 00:11:45,470
It's okay.

333
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,120
Officer Chen.

334
00:11:49,130 --> 00:11:49,840
Ms. Jiang,

335
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:51,560
what brings you here again?

336
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:52,960
I won't give up

337
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,670
until the case is solved.

338
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:56,910
If there's nothing else,

339
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:57,440
I'll be leaving then.

340
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:57,790
Okay.

341
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:58,560
Thank you.

342
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,320
Jiang Yan?

343
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:04,270
Zhou Cheng?

344
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,260
You've graduated?

345
00:12:11,030 --> 00:12:13,670
Yes, I'm working
in the prosecution office now.

346
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:15,270
You went to college in Hushi.

347
00:12:15,270 --> 00:12:17,510
Why did you come to Shengcheng
after graduation?

348
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:18,320
What about you?

349
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,600
Why are you in Shengcheng?

350
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,730
Because of Xiaolan.

351
00:12:27,390 --> 00:12:28,250
Mr. Huo, right?

352
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,200
Hello.

353
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:31,080
I'm Liu Yong from Yuanhui.

354
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:32,440
Nice to meet you.

355
00:12:32,550 --> 00:12:33,610
Please have a seat.

356
00:12:33,630 --> 00:12:34,080
Okay.

357
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:35,200
Thanks.

358
00:12:41,270 --> 00:12:42,730
I'll cut to the chase then.

359
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:44,790
Actually, someone's already working

360
00:12:44,790 --> 00:12:46,390
on the Haihua Hotel project.

361
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:47,750
But when I heard

362
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,000
that the designs of this guesthouse

363
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,460
were proposed by Yuanhui,

364
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,080
I was pleasantly surprised.

365
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,580
It was really unexpected.

366
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:58,280
Yuanhui isn't a big operation.

367
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,700
Before this guesthouse project,

368
00:13:00,910 --> 00:13:02,040
it mainly focused on

369
00:13:02,390 --> 00:13:03,920
home interior decoration.

370
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:05,870
That said, I really like

371
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:07,930
the overall style of the guesthouse.

372
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:08,670
If...

373
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,600
I mean, hypothetically,

374
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,670
if your designs

375
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,390
are adopted

376
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:16,150
for the Haihua Hotel project,

377
00:13:16,630 --> 00:13:17,290
I'll gladly

378
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:20,690
spare one-quarter of the renovation work

379
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:21,720
for you.

380
00:13:27,870 --> 00:13:29,400
You must be Ms. Xia Xiaolan.

381
00:13:30,270 --> 00:13:30,910
Ms. Xia,

382
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,560
are you satisfied...

383
00:13:32,630 --> 00:13:33,490
with this plan?

384
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:34,200
Mr. Huo,

385
00:13:34,510 --> 00:13:35,910
you're probably mistaken.

386
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:37,720
Yuanhui is in the charge of my uncle.

387
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,080
The gentleman sitting next to me

388
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:39,750
is Gong Yang,

389
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:41,010
a designer at Yuanhui.

390
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:43,570
I might participate in the revisions,

391
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,030
but you'll have to talk to my uncle

392
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:47,160
about the details of the cooperation.

393
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:49,320
Mr. Huo, you're offering Yuanhui

394
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,550
one quarter of the Haihua Hotel

395
00:13:50,550 --> 00:13:51,550
renovation work.

396
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:53,630
I truly appreciate your sincerity.

397
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:54,510
For us, this is

398
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:56,240
a great learning opportunity.

399
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,600
I'm wondering

400
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:58,750
if you can show us

401
00:13:58,750 --> 00:14:00,010
the previous designs.

402
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:01,720
Of course.

403
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:33,420
Mr. Huo,

404
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,270
we can modify the designs,

405
00:14:35,270 --> 00:14:36,960
but we need some time

406
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,360
and your support.

407
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:40,910
To be honest,

408
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:41,910
these designs

409
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:43,480
are already perfect.

410
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:45,630
If the hotel is renovated
following this plan,

411
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:46,700
I'm sure it will meet

412
00:14:46,700 --> 00:14:48,700
the standards of a five-star hotel.

413
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:49,990
May I ask

414
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,810
who came up with these designs?

415
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:55,200
Ms. Xia, you do have a good eye.

416
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:57,350
Actually, these designs

417
00:14:57,350 --> 00:14:59,150
don't need to be modified at all,

418
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:01,120
since they pair well

419
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:03,380
with the main buildings of Haihua Hotel.

420
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:05,120
Ms. Xia, you studied architecture.

421
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:05,960
I bet

422
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,490
you have heard about Mr. Mao Kangshan.

423
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,060
This...

424
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,150
is a work by Mr. Mao.

425
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,600
Mr. Mao really is a master.

426
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:16,120
Such brilliant designs.

427
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:18,060
Ahead in aesthetic taste as well.

428
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:20,240
How odd.

429
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,550
Why would anyone want to modify

430
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:23,010
a master's work like this?

431
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,440
Essentially,

432
00:15:24,510 --> 00:15:26,550
it's not an issue
with the design proposal.

433
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,440
It's a struggle for the rights

434
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:28,550
to manage the hotel.

435
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:30,480
Dongfeng Holdings doesn't have
the upper hand now.

436
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:32,630
But this is Master Mao's work.

437
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,330
If Yuanhui modifies it,

438
00:15:34,390 --> 00:15:35,750
its reputation in the architecture circle

439
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:37,210
will be damaged, won't it?

440
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:38,720
Yes.

441
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:39,870
Mr. Mao is reputed
as the architectural leader

442
00:15:39,870 --> 00:15:41,630
in the south, and Mr. Ning the north.

443
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:42,320
By Mr. Ning,

444
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,550
I mean Mr. Mao's counterpart,

445
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:44,360
Ning Yanfan.

446
00:15:44,910 --> 00:15:45,750
At first, they were

447
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:47,550
on equal footing in the field.

448
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:48,920
But in recent years,

449
00:15:49,030 --> 00:15:50,360
Mr. Ning has gained much prestige

450
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:52,320
both internationally and domestically.

451
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:53,600
Meanwhile, Mr. Mao Kangshan

452
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:55,150
is known as a reclusive master

453
00:15:55,150 --> 00:15:57,030
by Hangcheng design institutes.

454
00:15:57,630 --> 00:15:58,080
Uncle,

455
00:15:58,360 --> 00:15:59,510
do you know why?

456
00:16:00,390 --> 00:16:02,320
Because Mr. Mao is indifferent to fame?

457
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:04,150
That's because
Mr. Mao has a stranger temper

458
00:16:04,150 --> 00:16:05,210
and is quite moody.

459
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:07,240
He's getting more and more
self-centered, too.

460
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:09,150
I heard that he doesn't take
apprentices anymore.

461
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:09,840
He does most of the work

462
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,630
on his own.

463
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:12,630
I guess he must've poured

464
00:16:12,630 --> 00:16:13,600
his heart and soul

465
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:15,330
into the Haihua Hotel project.

466
00:16:15,550 --> 00:16:17,360
Mr. Huo says Mr. Mao agrees
to have his designs revised now,

467
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:19,750
but who knows
if he'll change his mind later?

468
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:21,910
Mr. Huo looks quite young.

469
00:16:21,910 --> 00:16:22,790
I'm not sure

470
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:24,080
how reliable his words are.

471
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,270
If this old man

472
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:27,030
is really that eccentric,

473
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:29,870
there might be a change of situation.

474
00:16:29,870 --> 00:16:31,480
That said, no matter what,

475
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:32,960
this is a good opportunity for us.

476
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:33,560
Gong Yang,

477
00:16:33,790 --> 00:16:35,360
spend the next few days
reviewing the designs

478
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,510
of domestic and foreign hotels.

479
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:37,270
Learn from them.

480
00:16:37,270 --> 00:16:37,670
Got it.

481
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:40,720
Mr. Huo attempts
to gain controlling rights

482
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,320
through a revised proposal.

483
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,390
And we in Yuanhui

484
00:16:43,630 --> 00:16:44,910
can also use it

485
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,580
to achieve bigger dreams.

486
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:51,130
[Zhiyuan Law Firm]

487
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:51,200
That's a very dangerous move of yours.

488
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,600
You are a lawyer.

489
00:16:52,670 --> 00:16:53,270
You can't always

490
00:16:53,270 --> 00:16:54,840
let emotions cloud your judgement!

491
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,360
Exactly because I am a lawyer,

492
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,600
I must thoroughly investigate this matter

493
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:58,860
and uncover the truth.

494
00:16:59,150 --> 00:17:00,550
It was an accident,

495
00:17:00,550 --> 00:17:01,960
as I've told you many times.

496
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,550
What truth are you trying to uncover?

497
00:17:03,550 --> 00:17:04,109
Was it so?

498
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:06,069
Was it really an accident?

499
00:17:06,069 --> 00:17:07,000
On that very day,

500
00:17:07,349 --> 00:17:08,240
someone asked us to meet

501
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,480
at the construction site to tell us

502
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,720
a lead on the smuggling case.

503
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,069
Was it really a coincidence

504
00:17:12,069 --> 00:17:14,030
that danger happened when we just arrived?

505
00:17:14,030 --> 00:17:15,160
That suspicious temp worker

506
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,400
has never shown up again.

507
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:17,920
It's been almost two years.

508
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,069
Fewer and fewer of the workers

509
00:17:19,069 --> 00:17:20,310
from back then can be found now.

510
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:21,310
Do you really think

511
00:17:21,310 --> 00:17:22,770
that was just an accident?

512
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,079
Come here.

513
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:30,110
Do you dare say before Shi Kai's desk

514
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:32,240
that his death was purely accidental?

515
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:36,200
Senior,

516
00:17:39,110 --> 00:17:40,790
I won't let my work be affected.

517
00:17:40,790 --> 00:17:41,480
But I am determined

518
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:43,410
to get to the bottom of this matter.

519
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:45,070
You'll head to Hangcheng
for a business trip tomorrow

520
00:17:45,070 --> 00:17:46,110
to go over the contract details

521
00:17:46,110 --> 00:17:47,040
with the client.

522
00:17:47,550 --> 00:17:48,070
Senior!

523
00:17:48,270 --> 00:17:48,720
Didn't you say

524
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:49,790
you wouldn't let your work be affected?

525
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:51,450
This is not up for discussion!

526
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:09,690
Here come

527
00:18:09,830 --> 00:18:10,550
the noodles.

528
00:18:10,550 --> 00:18:11,080
Try some.

529
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:12,100
Hang on.

530
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:13,550
Let me put these away.

531
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:17,310
Try it.

532
00:18:19,550 --> 00:18:20,410
Smells so good.

533
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:24,710
Take this.

534
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:26,170
It's well mixed.

535
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:31,040
Give it a try.

536
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:34,750
So tasty.

537
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:35,580
Tasty, huh?

538
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:40,360
Did you lock the door?

539
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,400
They won't barge in later,

540
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:42,110
will they?

541
00:18:44,550 --> 00:18:45,070
Wei said

542
00:18:45,070 --> 00:18:46,350
they'd do inventory tonight.

543
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:47,880
So they won't be back early.

544
00:18:53,750 --> 00:18:54,160
We're leaving.

545
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:54,720
Bye, guys.

546
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:55,070
See you tomorrow.

547
00:18:55,070 --> 00:18:56,030
Good work today. See you tomorrow.

548
00:18:56,030 --> 00:18:56,550
Bye.

549
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:58,270
Bai!

550
00:18:58,880 --> 00:18:59,310
Kang.

551
00:18:59,550 --> 00:19:00,080
Mr. Xiao.

552
00:19:00,590 --> 00:19:01,120
Mr. Xiao.

553
00:19:01,270 --> 00:19:02,310
I ordered from you because I have faith

554
00:19:02,310 --> 00:19:03,660
in the quality of your products.

555
00:19:03,660 --> 00:19:04,640
But the furniture I bought here

556
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,830
warped in less than three months.

557
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:06,960
What was that about?

558
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:07,830
I'm so sorry.

559
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:08,240
My apologies,

560
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:08,770
Mr. Xiao.

561
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:09,730
Don't worry.

562
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:10,690
We will take

563
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:11,790
full responsibility

564
00:19:11,790 --> 00:19:13,400
for all orders placed with us.

565
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,400
Look,

566
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:15,310
it's already nighttime.

567
00:19:15,310 --> 00:19:16,070
Tomorrow morning,

568
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:17,000
I'll quickly go to your place

569
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:17,890
to check out on the items.

570
00:19:17,890 --> 00:19:18,920
Then we'll discuss

571
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,480
what to do.

572
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:20,210
Is that okay?

573
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:21,440
Fine.

574
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:23,160
Come to my place tomorrow morning then.

575
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:23,790
Sure thing.

576
00:19:23,790 --> 00:19:24,400
Anyway, I demand

577
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,260
replacements.

578
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:25,790
You got it.

579
00:19:25,790 --> 00:19:26,640
Rest assured, Mr. Xiao.

580
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:27,920
Here at Happy Home Materials,

581
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:29,720
we fully guarantee the quality.

582
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:31,670
Alright, I'll take off then.

583
00:19:32,150 --> 00:19:32,590
Okay, bye.

584
00:19:32,590 --> 00:19:33,720
Take care, Mr. Xiao.

585
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:35,890
Let me check.

586
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,720
What happened?

587
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:39,830
The ledger?

588
00:19:39,830 --> 00:19:40,510
This is the one.

589
00:19:40,510 --> 00:19:41,750
This is

590
00:19:42,030 --> 00:19:43,550
Mr. Xiao's order history,

591
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:45,620
from the opening day till now.

592
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,640
Let's take a look.

593
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:48,110
Mr. Xiao has placed

594
00:19:48,270 --> 00:19:49,480
many orders with us.

595
00:19:49,550 --> 00:19:49,920
Yes.

596
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:51,350
Hardware, bathroom fixtures, and materials

597
00:19:51,350 --> 00:19:52,110
like panels.

598
00:19:52,350 --> 00:19:54,350
Look at these two orders for panels.

599
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:56,080
They were both handled by Shao.

600
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,640
Look at these two orders.

601
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:59,270
They were placed and canceled

602
00:19:59,270 --> 00:20:00,510
on the same day.

603
00:20:01,110 --> 00:20:02,570
This is indeed a bit weird.

604
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:03,680
Shall we ask Xiaolan

605
00:20:03,680 --> 00:20:04,880
what to do about this?

606
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:06,350
Ask Xiaolan?

607
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:08,750
She's your friend, not your mother.

608
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:09,750
We can't ask her all the time,

609
00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:10,440
or when will the two of us

610
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:11,240
truly grow?

611
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:12,240
Got it.

612
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:21,310
Are you in a bad mood today?

613
00:20:23,030 --> 00:20:23,720
No, I'm not.

614
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:26,250
I just had a little dispute

615
00:20:26,310 --> 00:20:27,110
with my senior

616
00:20:27,830 --> 00:20:28,590
on a case.

617
00:20:30,320 --> 00:20:31,650
You don't usually

618
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:32,680
bring home

619
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:34,140
the negativity from work.

620
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,970
You mean Shi Kai's case, right?

621
00:20:41,750 --> 00:20:43,280
It's been nearly two years.

622
00:20:43,440 --> 00:20:44,310
But there hasn't been a lead

623
00:20:44,310 --> 00:20:45,440
on that temp worker.

624
00:20:46,590 --> 00:20:47,550
My senior keeps trying to convince me

625
00:20:47,550 --> 00:20:49,080
that it was just an accident

626
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:51,460
and stopping me from probing deeper.

627
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:53,000
I planned to visit the construction crew

628
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,460
tomorrow, yet he insisted

629
00:20:54,510 --> 00:20:56,510
I go to Hangcheng on a business trip.

630
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:58,400
In fact, that Hangcheng contract

631
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,680
has been going very smoothly.

632
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:01,480
There's no need for a trip at all.

633
00:21:02,790 --> 00:21:05,270
Hangcheng is a lovely place.

634
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:09,380
Zhou Cheng,

635
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,640
now that you're in a bad mood,

636
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,640
how about I accompany you to Hangcheng

637
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,030
where we can relax a bit?

638
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:20,070
Are you trying to keep me company,

639
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:21,400
or...

640
00:21:23,030 --> 00:21:23,880
Fine.

641
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:25,270
To be frank,

642
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:27,800
I'm going to visit
an eccentric old man there.

643
00:21:28,180 --> 00:21:29,510
What eccentric old man?

644
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:32,340
You'll know when we get there.

645
00:21:35,430 --> 00:21:39,650
[Hangcheng]
[No. 1 Architectural Design  Institute]

646
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:37,510
Hello.

647
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:39,610
I'm here to meet Mr. Mao Kangshan.

648
00:21:39,750 --> 00:21:40,950
Mr. Mao isn't around.

649
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:42,480
He never meets anyone

650
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:43,550
without an appointment.

651
00:21:43,550 --> 00:21:44,400
I'll make one then.

652
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:45,800
May I ask where to do that?

653
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:46,740
Appointments?

654
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:49,130
We don't offer that service here.

655
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:51,310
No meetings without an appointment

656
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:52,790
and no way to make an appointment.

657
00:21:52,790 --> 00:21:55,320
Mr. Mao is clearly
not giving anyone a chance.

658
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,270
You're right.

659
00:21:56,590 --> 00:21:58,030
He just hates to meet people like you

660
00:21:58,030 --> 00:21:59,240
who harbor ulterior motives.

661
00:21:59,240 --> 00:21:59,720
Leave.

662
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:01,180
Don't come here again.

663
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:05,070
I'll have one more talk

664
00:22:05,070 --> 00:22:06,240
with Yaxing Foreign Trading

665
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,550
to flesh out the contract soon.

666
00:22:07,550 --> 00:22:07,960
Okay.

667
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,330
Thank you, Mr. Zhou,

668
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:10,960
for making a trip.

669
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:12,110
No problem. It's my job.

670
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:12,910
Thanks again.

671
00:22:18,550 --> 00:22:18,960
This is

672
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,590
a work by a master architect in Hangcheng,

673
00:22:20,590 --> 00:22:22,050
who is named Mao Kangshan.

674
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,600
It's a real treasure.

675
00:22:26,350 --> 00:22:27,610
I heard Mr. Mao's works

676
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:29,720
are rarely found on the market.

677
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:30,120
Right.

678
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:30,970
This was

679
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,640
created by him when he was young.

680
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:33,350
My family has been

681
00:22:33,350 --> 00:22:34,960
friends with Mr. Mao's for generations,

682
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,890
so I've known him since childhood.

683
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:56,500
I can remember fewer and fewer things
from the past.

684
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:58,250
Will there be a day when I...

685
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:01,640
Come in!

686
00:23:10,590 --> 00:23:11,520
Anything wrong?

687
00:23:11,650 --> 00:23:12,580
You had a bad day?

688
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:14,350
The institute wouldn't let me in.

689
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:15,720
I plan to try my luck
at the family quarters

690
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:16,400
tomorrow.

691
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:19,330
I know it's not a proper thing to do,

692
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:20,510
yet I just can't quit

693
00:23:20,510 --> 00:23:21,840
before meeting Mr. Mao.

694
00:23:22,110 --> 00:23:23,640
I heard that he would chase away

695
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:24,790
all visitors to his place.

696
00:23:24,790 --> 00:23:26,200
I'm not sure if I'll be able

697
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:28,200
to get him to open the door tomorrow.

698
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:30,370
I have a piece of news

699
00:23:30,830 --> 00:23:31,790
about Mr. Mao.

700
00:23:32,150 --> 00:23:32,830
Tell me now.

701
00:23:46,210 --> 00:23:47,470
Trimming vegetables?

702
00:23:47,510 --> 00:23:48,240
Yes.

703
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:51,550
I'm going to dry these on this sunny day.

704
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:52,350
Hello.

705
00:23:52,920 --> 00:23:53,510
May I ask

706
00:23:53,510 --> 00:23:54,350
if Mr. Mao Kangshan

707
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:55,200
lives here?

708
00:23:55,550 --> 00:23:56,110
Yes.

709
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:58,000
Why are you looking for him?

710
00:23:58,830 --> 00:23:59,430
Well, I...

711
00:24:00,310 --> 00:24:00,970
Zhou Cheng!

712
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:02,530
Is it heavy? Let me help.

713
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:03,210
Not at all.

714
00:24:03,210 --> 00:24:03,720
It's confirmed

715
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:05,050
that Mr. Mao lives here.

716
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:06,750
Yes, he does.

717
00:24:06,750 --> 00:24:07,590
Mr. Mao Kangshan

718
00:24:07,590 --> 00:24:08,990
lives on the sixth floor.

719
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:10,070
We'd hate to bother you...

720
00:24:10,070 --> 00:24:10,720
I'm going upstairs anyway.

721
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:11,790
Let me take you to his place.

722
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:12,240
Thank you.

723
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:12,770
Let's go.

724
00:24:20,510 --> 00:24:22,720
What was the provincial institute
thinking?

725
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:23,920
Did they not consider

726
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:25,000
Mr. Mao's age at all

727
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:26,260
when they assigned him

728
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:27,900
a sixth-floor apartment?

729
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:30,270
I can imagine how inconvenient for him

730
00:24:30,270 --> 00:24:31,600
to go out for groceries.

731
00:24:31,750 --> 00:24:33,010
This is his apartment.

732
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,860
Knock on the door yourselves.

733
00:24:36,720 --> 00:24:37,520
Zheng Shuqin!

734
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:40,910
You're Mr. Mao's daughter-in-law, right?

735
00:24:41,310 --> 00:24:42,160
I know Mr. Mao

736
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:44,030
is reluctant to meet with strangers.

737
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,750
Can you knock on his door for me?

738
00:24:45,750 --> 00:24:47,410
Y-Y-You're asking me to do it?

739
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:50,920
How did you know who I am?

740
00:24:52,110 --> 00:24:52,880
Your story is well-known

741
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:55,200
at the povincial architectural institute.

742
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,270
I heard that they originally

743
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:57,400
assigned Mr. Mao

744
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:59,510
a large apartment on the third floor,

745
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,750
and his son, Mao Guosheng,

746
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:02,410
a small one on the sixth floor.

747
00:25:02,610 --> 00:25:03,400
But surprisingly,

748
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:04,720
you took the apartment on the third floor

749
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:06,920
and made Mr. Mao live on the sixth floor.

750
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:07,830
Hey, young lady,

751
00:25:07,830 --> 00:25:09,160
what's all that nonsense from?

752
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:10,510
Mr. Mao voluntarily let us

753
00:25:10,510 --> 00:25:11,550
take his apartment.

754
00:25:11,550 --> 00:25:12,200
Really?

755
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:13,680
But you didn't say

756
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:14,680
the exact reason.

757
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:15,550
Mr. Mao did it for the good

758
00:25:15,550 --> 00:25:16,640
of his grandson, didn't he?

759
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:18,560
Who would've known
you'd have the nerve to ask for it?

760
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:19,240
If I were you,

761
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,830
I couldn't have been so thick-skinned.

762
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:22,070
Who are you calling thick-skinned?

763
00:25:22,070 --> 00:25:23,160
Stop arguing at my door.

764
00:25:23,160 --> 00:25:23,880
This is annoying.

765
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:24,510
Go away!

766
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:25,920
Mr. Mao.

767
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:27,480
What?

768
00:25:28,110 --> 00:25:29,680
Are you forcing your way into my home?

769
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,350
We're terribly sorry, Mr. Mao.

770
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,550
We had no choice

771
00:25:32,790 --> 00:25:33,880
but to show up at your door

772
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:34,680
so abruptly.

773
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:35,920
Mr. Mao,

774
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:37,510
we are here for the Haihua Hotel

775
00:25:37,510 --> 00:25:38,400
project.

776
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:39,970
All I need is 10 minutes.

777
00:25:40,790 --> 00:25:41,850
What are these for?

778
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:44,200
Well, you see,

779
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:45,400
this is my first visit.

780
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:46,640
I can't show up empty-handed, right?

781
00:25:46,640 --> 00:25:48,200
I'd like you to take these gifts
and be my tutor.

782
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:50,260
Did anyone say I'd take apprentices?

783
00:25:50,270 --> 00:25:51,400
D-Do I even know you?

784
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,450
Let me introduce myself then.

785
00:25:54,070 --> 00:25:54,930
Hello, Mr. Mao.

786
00:25:55,030 --> 00:25:56,290
My name is Xia Xiaolan.

787
00:25:56,350 --> 00:25:57,880
I do renovation work in Shengcheng.

788
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:58,920
The company I'm in will take part

789
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:00,520
in the Haihua Hotel project.

790
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:01,590
I've agreed

791
00:26:01,590 --> 00:26:03,070
to have my designs modified.

792
00:26:03,070 --> 00:26:04,070
You may leave now.

793
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:05,350
Mr. Mao.

794
00:26:06,270 --> 00:26:07,200
Everyone outside says

795
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,660
you have a strange temper.

796
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:09,750
But to my knowledge,

797
00:26:09,750 --> 00:26:11,070
you not only possess great talent,

798
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:12,330
but great virtues too.

799
00:26:12,510 --> 00:26:13,270
The renovation of Haihua Hotel

800
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:14,670
is a commercial project.

801
00:26:14,750 --> 00:26:16,110
Out of respect for the contract

802
00:26:16,110 --> 00:26:17,310
and your work partners,

803
00:26:17,310 --> 00:26:18,920
you agreed to have the designs modified,

804
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,240
even though you knew

805
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:21,800
there was nothing wrong.

806
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,160
So, today, I'm here

807
00:26:25,310 --> 00:26:26,790
not only to talk to you

808
00:26:26,790 --> 00:26:27,920
about Haihua Hotel.

809
00:26:28,510 --> 00:26:29,480
Shengcheng

810
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:31,140
is a rapidly developing city.

811
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,910
Every day, there are new buildings,

812
00:26:32,910 --> 00:26:33,880
new opportunities,

813
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:34,790
and new dreams.

814
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:39,200
I'd like to talk to you about the future.

815
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:46,180
Hurry.

816
00:26:52,350 --> 00:26:53,830
It's been a long time
since someone had the guts

817
00:26:53,830 --> 00:26:55,070
to bring gifts to your father-in-law.

818
00:26:55,070 --> 00:26:57,110
Aren't they afraid of being kicked out?

819
00:26:57,110 --> 00:26:58,200
This is really odd.

820
00:26:58,750 --> 00:27:00,680
What a shock they're still in there.

821
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:02,280
What are they talking about?

822
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:16,220
Tell me about your idea of the future.

823
00:27:24,870 --> 00:27:26,280
[Qihang Architectural Design Firm
Retainer Agreement]

824
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:33,960
You're planning to start

825
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:35,620
your own architectural firm?

826
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:36,240
Yes.

827
00:27:37,210 --> 00:27:37,840
Mr. Mao,

828
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:40,240
I know you are not only talented,

829
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:41,830
but also aspired to cultivate

830
00:27:41,830 --> 00:27:42,550
the next generation

831
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:44,000
of architects for the industry.

832
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:45,400
So, this time, I came here

833
00:27:45,460 --> 00:27:47,160
with the hope of you serving as the pillar

834
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:49,420
of my architectural firm in Shengcheng.

835
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:51,110
I hope that one day,

836
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:52,240
my firm can grow

837
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:53,640
to be like the foreign ones

838
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:55,960
and become a dream place
and a starting point

839
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:57,310
for all architects.

840
00:27:59,830 --> 00:28:00,640
Do you know...

841
00:28:01,510 --> 00:28:03,910
what ambitious remarks you're saying now?

842
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:05,540
Yes, I know.

843
00:28:06,270 --> 00:28:07,920
I graduated only two years ago.

844
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:09,200
It's fair to say I haven't really

845
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:10,000
crossed the threshold

846
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:11,000
of this industry.

847
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:13,720
Yet here I am,
saying something like a fantasy.

848
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:15,050
The old me wouldn't have

849
00:28:15,110 --> 00:28:16,640
dared make a dream this big.

850
00:28:17,070 --> 00:28:17,640
But if

851
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,680
we don't aim high,

852
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:19,880
how do we know

853
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,110
if we're able to make our dreams

854
00:28:21,110 --> 00:28:21,790
come true?

855
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,200
There are ice pops in the fridge.

856
00:28:26,200 --> 00:28:27,110
Help yourself.

857
00:28:27,350 --> 00:28:28,210
Thanks, but no.

858
00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:29,650
Would you like one?

859
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:32,150
Mr. Mao,

860
00:28:33,110 --> 00:28:34,710
I believe you aren't content

861
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:35,590
to just be

862
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:37,190
a reclusive master, are you?

863
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:44,960
I've got you

864
00:28:45,030 --> 00:28:46,590
all the panel samples

865
00:28:46,590 --> 00:28:47,680
you picked last time.

866
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,010
Okay.

867
00:28:48,750 --> 00:28:49,480
Hey, Shao,

868
00:28:49,680 --> 00:28:50,940
-come over.
-Mr. Kang.

869
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:51,960
Give Ms. Wei here

870
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,350
a detailed introduction

871
00:28:53,350 --> 00:28:54,400
on our panels.

872
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:55,070
Sure, Mr. Kang.

873
00:28:55,070 --> 00:28:55,400
Please.

874
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:55,750
Okay.

875
00:28:55,830 --> 00:28:56,480
Ms. Wei, please.

876
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:56,810
Okay.

877
00:28:57,550 --> 00:28:58,110
Ms. Wei, look.

878
00:28:58,110 --> 00:28:59,440
These three types of panels

879
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:00,750
are what you chose last time.

880
00:29:00,750 --> 00:29:01,110
Yes.

881
00:29:01,110 --> 00:29:01,920
They come in

882
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:02,920
different sizes,

883
00:29:03,550 --> 00:29:05,000
materials,

884
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:06,160
and various

885
00:29:06,160 --> 00:29:06,880
colors.

886
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:08,030
If you're going for

887
00:29:08,030 --> 00:29:09,030
a simple, minimalist style

888
00:29:09,030 --> 00:29:10,510
for your home improvement project,

889
00:29:10,510 --> 00:29:11,480
I think this color

890
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:12,740
