891
00:29:13,070 --> 00:29:16,940
[Affordable and high-quality products
at Happy Home Materials]

892
00:29:13,330 --> 00:29:14,640
Shall we grab a bite after work?

893
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:15,200
Okay.

894
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:16,740
Bye, Ms. Bai, Mr. Kang.

895
00:29:17,070 --> 00:29:17,720
See you tomorrow.

896
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:18,270
Good work today.

897
00:29:18,270 --> 00:29:19,270
See you tomorrow.

898
00:29:19,310 --> 00:29:20,510
See you tomorrow, Ms. Bai, Mr. Kang.

899
00:29:20,510 --> 00:29:22,110
Good work. See you tomorrow.

900
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:30,440
I'll follow them.

901
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:31,550
Come after you lock up the doors.

902
00:29:31,550 --> 00:29:32,240
Be careful.

903
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:50,940
So this is a panel factory.

904
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:53,250
Shao really is the culprit.

905
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:04,640
T-They've outnumbered us.

906
00:30:05,550 --> 00:30:06,150
Sis Bai...

907
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,000
Sis Bai?

908
00:30:10,550 --> 00:30:10,880
Yes.

909
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:11,800
Come now.

910
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:18,030
You scared me.

911
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:18,830
What were you doing?

912
00:30:18,830 --> 00:30:19,920
Calling for backup.

913
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:20,680
Smart move.

914
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:22,570
I've figured it out.

915
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:23,750
Shao faked those

916
00:30:23,750 --> 00:30:24,880
canceled order records,

917
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:25,480
and had this factory

918
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:26,960
make the products in secret.

919
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:27,590
He then sent

920
00:30:27,590 --> 00:30:28,550
the shoddy goods to the client

921
00:30:28,550 --> 00:30:30,550
in the name of Happy Home Materials.

922
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:34,010
What are you two doing?

923
00:30:34,070 --> 00:30:35,110
You seem sneaky.

924
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:35,760
Come over!

925
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,270
-Where’s the backup?
-Come here now!

926
00:30:37,270 --> 00:30:38,070
Not here yet.

927
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:40,470
Who would've known
we'd get caught so soon?

928
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:43,160
You're director of the factory, right?

929
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:45,680
Well, I'd like to place an order.

930
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,030
But we need a massive number

931
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:47,760
of products.

932
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:48,510
I wonder

933
00:30:48,510 --> 00:30:50,170
if your factory can handle it.

934
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:51,740
Place an order?

935
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:53,310
For what?

936
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:54,440
Isn't your factory...

937
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:54,920
Uncle!

938
00:30:56,110 --> 00:30:56,840
Those two...

939
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:57,920
are Mr. Kang and Mr. Bai

940
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,510
from the Happy Home Materials!

941
00:30:59,510 --> 00:31:00,920
What? You're such

942
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:01,580
an ingrate.

943
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,890
Now that you've recognized Shao,

944
00:31:05,350 --> 00:31:07,480
I have one more reason not to let you go.

945
00:31:07,750 --> 00:31:08,610
Take them down!

946
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:13,100
Stop, or you'll regret it!

947
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:16,440
Only San is here to back us up?

948
00:31:16,440 --> 00:31:17,840
He's all the help we need.

949
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:24,160
If you dare to attack,

950
00:31:24,310 --> 00:31:25,910
I'll fight in self-defense!

951
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:29,350
Wait.

952
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:30,720
Who are you?

953
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:32,800
What are you waiting for?

954
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:33,960
Go get him!

955
00:31:48,570 --> 00:31:49,430
Quick, hit him!

956
00:31:49,750 --> 00:31:50,410
Beat him up!

957
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:52,070
Go get...

958
00:32:19,030 --> 00:32:19,490
Hit him!

959
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:46,550
Here we are! Here!

960
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,480
-Freeze!
-Nobody move!

961
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:49,210
Arrest them!

962
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:51,830
Get up!

963
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:53,920
You, get up!

964
00:32:55,310 --> 00:32:56,570
-Don't move!
-Behave!

965
00:32:56,750 --> 00:32:57,350
Cuff them!

966
00:33:00,030 --> 00:33:01,160
You're fired.

967
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:05,680
A lawyer's letter will find you.

968
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:11,800
I told you not to make me fight
in self-defense.

969
00:33:12,270 --> 00:33:12,640
Go!

970
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:14,810
Behave, you lot!

971
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:16,160
Go!

972
00:33:19,590 --> 00:33:20,120
Let's go.

973
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:36,560
What now?

974
00:33:36,830 --> 00:33:38,090
Have you warmed up yet?

975
00:33:38,240 --> 00:33:39,240
Let's test it out.

976
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:40,210
Off we go!

977
00:33:43,070 --> 00:33:43,640
Wei,

978
00:33:43,910 --> 00:33:44,680
go home yourself.

979
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:46,350
I'm heading to the boxing gym with San.

980
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:47,180
Okay, got it.

981
00:33:56,590 --> 00:33:57,590
The two of them...

982
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:59,280
have such strong physiques.

983
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:00,790
Not bad.

984
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:01,850
The two of you

985
00:34:01,860 --> 00:34:03,460
can fend for yourselves now.

986
00:34:03,550 --> 00:34:04,080
Alright.

987
00:34:04,270 --> 00:34:05,670
We'll talk when I'm back.

988
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:06,640
Bye.

989
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:09,190
Was that Zhenzhu?

990
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:09,760
Yes.

991
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:12,320
Shao, an employee of the materials store,

992
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:13,230
colluded with a relative of his

993
00:34:13,230 --> 00:34:14,280
to pass off shoddy goods as quality ones.

994
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:15,940
Sis Bai and Wei took them down.

995
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:17,030
Wei already bragged to me

996
00:34:17,030 --> 00:34:18,400
about it for quite a while.

997
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:19,070
Shall we hang out

998
00:34:19,070 --> 00:34:20,230
in Hangcheng in the next two days?

999
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:21,030
We can go back to Shengcheng

1000
00:34:21,030 --> 00:34:22,820
with Mr. Mao when he agrees to join us.

1001
00:34:22,820 --> 00:34:24,820
But he hasn't nodded yet.

1002
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:26,000
What gives you that confidence?

1003
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:27,659
I just have confidence in you.

1004
00:34:31,070 --> 00:34:31,440
Look.

1005
00:34:31,750 --> 00:34:33,000
Isn't it pretty over there?

1006
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:33,460
This...

1007
00:34:33,670 --> 00:34:34,870
is really beautiful.

1008
00:34:36,030 --> 00:34:37,889
Look at that Dingsheng cake shop.

1009
00:34:37,960 --> 00:34:39,150
What a queue of people.

1010
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:40,150
It's auspicuous,

1011
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:41,440
since this cake symbolizes victory.

1012
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:42,440
Why don't we buy some?

1013
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:42,800
Sure.

1014
00:34:43,190 --> 00:34:44,320
I'll go check it out.

1015
00:34:52,550 --> 00:34:53,190
Xiaolan?

1016
00:34:59,150 --> 00:34:59,880
Xiaolan?

1017
00:35:05,670 --> 00:35:06,400
Xiaolan?

1018
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:12,230
Gosh. You gave me such a fright!

1019
00:35:12,920 --> 00:35:14,320
Come on, have some water.

1020
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:15,530
Xiaolan,

1021
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:16,710
is it fun in Hangcheng?

1022
00:35:16,710 --> 00:35:17,910
Slow down. Easy on it.

1023
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:18,710
Yes.

1024
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:19,290
Fun, huh?

1025
00:35:19,590 --> 00:35:20,520
Then from now on,

1026
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:21,590
let's have

1027
00:35:21,590 --> 00:35:22,990
a family trip every year.

1028
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,120
Hangcheng...

1029
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:27,000
I visited Hangcheng with Mom and Dad
years ago.

1030
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:28,930
Xiaolan, you must be tired, right?

1031
00:35:29,070 --> 00:35:29,530
Come on.

1032
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,400
I'll carry you on my back.

1033
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:31,930
Careful.

1034
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:58,480
[Hoxter Clocks and Watches]

1035
00:36:00,510 --> 00:36:01,510
Come in for a look.

1036
00:36:07,480 --> 00:36:08,480
Pick one you like.

1037
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:18,800
You like this?

1038
00:36:19,110 --> 00:36:20,670
You do have a good eye, miss.

1039
00:36:21,030 --> 00:36:22,290
It's an imported good.

1040
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,180
You can't buy it

1041
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:24,090
anywhere else.

1042
00:36:26,510 --> 00:36:26,960
One.

1043
00:36:27,670 --> 00:36:28,110
Two.

1044
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:29,320
Three.

1045
00:36:32,510 --> 00:36:33,550
It's so pretty!

1046
00:36:34,030 --> 00:36:34,560
Isn't it?

1047
00:36:34,710 --> 00:36:35,320
Yes, it is.

1048
00:36:38,230 --> 00:36:39,290
Alright, careful!

1049
00:36:46,190 --> 00:36:46,850
You like it?

1050
00:36:47,110 --> 00:36:48,310
If you do, buy it then.

1051
00:36:49,030 --> 00:36:50,650
You seem to really like alarm clocks.

1052
00:36:50,650 --> 00:36:51,630
You were buying an alarm clock

1053
00:36:51,630 --> 00:36:52,760
when I first met you.

1054
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:53,780
I won't take it.

1055
00:36:53,810 --> 00:36:54,740
Thanks, though.

1056
00:36:56,280 --> 00:36:57,140
Why not buy one?

1057
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:11,190
How is it? Beautiful, right?

1058
00:37:11,190 --> 00:37:11,590
Yes.

1059
00:37:13,550 --> 00:37:15,110
Which is prettier, me or the scenery?

1060
00:37:15,110 --> 00:37:15,550
You.

1061
00:37:19,710 --> 00:37:21,480
There used to stand the Leifeng Pagoda,
right?

1062
00:37:21,480 --> 00:37:21,880
Right.

1063
00:37:22,630 --> 00:37:24,190
It's a pity that it collapsed long ago.

1064
00:37:24,190 --> 00:37:25,850
Luckily, the story survived.

1065
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:28,630
Bai Suzhen the snake spirit

1066
00:37:28,630 --> 00:37:29,230
and Xu Xian were

1067
00:37:29,230 --> 00:37:30,760
from different worlds to begin with.

1068
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:31,710
Despite the huge difference,

1069
00:37:31,710 --> 00:37:33,710
they fell for each other
against heaven's will.

1070
00:37:33,710 --> 00:37:35,310
Bai Suzhen paid a steep price

1071
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:38,070
by being trapped in the Leifeng Pagoda
for 18 years.

1072
00:37:38,070 --> 00:37:38,930
Was it worth it?

1073
00:37:39,670 --> 00:37:40,800
Sometimes, it is

1074
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:42,480
through hardships

1075
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:44,210
that love shows its true worth.

1076
00:37:44,710 --> 00:37:46,310
But I don't need to go through

1077
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:48,000
hardships to realize

1078
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:51,080
that you're the most precious of all
in my life.

1079
00:37:56,190 --> 00:37:56,720
Xiaolan,

1080
00:37:58,630 --> 00:37:59,690
let's get married.

1081
00:38:02,710 --> 00:38:03,710
Didn't we agree

1082
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:05,800
to register for marriage

1083
00:38:06,070 --> 00:38:07,400
when Luna had 50 stores?

1084
00:38:07,710 --> 00:38:09,640
It should be about time now, right?

1085
00:38:10,590 --> 00:38:11,250
Zhou Cheng,

1086
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,880
when I completely

1087
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:14,610
hand over Luna to Chen Xiliang,

1088
00:38:15,070 --> 00:38:16,000
let's register for marriage.

1089
00:38:15,600 --> 00:38:21,560
♪ Watching the flowers fall,
lonely I ask the night sky ♪

1090
00:38:17,590 --> 00:38:18,120
Shall we?

1091
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:20,590
I can't believe

1092
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:21,900
I nearly forgot it.

1093
00:38:22,220 --> 00:38:27,440
♪ Is spring hazy where you are? ♪

1094
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:23,840
Sure.

1095
00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:25,380
Let's get married.

1096
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:26,840
Great.

1097
00:38:29,100 --> 00:38:32,050
♪ Time is so stingy ♪

1098
00:38:32,070 --> 00:38:35,420
♪ It takes away even the memories ♪

1099
00:38:36,310 --> 00:38:38,920
♪ But I still remember ♪

1100
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:39,320
Xiaolan,

1101
00:38:39,110 --> 00:38:43,390
♪ The promises of love ♪

1102
00:38:40,710 --> 00:38:42,570
are you worried about something?

1103
00:38:43,590 --> 00:38:46,050
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

1104
00:38:46,070 --> 00:38:50,780
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

1105
00:38:50,810 --> 00:38:53,370
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

1106
00:38:53,390 --> 00:38:57,940
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

1107
00:38:58,420 --> 00:39:02,190
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

1108
00:39:02,210 --> 00:39:06,420
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

1109
00:39:02,510 --> 00:39:04,030
From forgetting who I was

1110
00:39:05,110 --> 00:39:06,710
to forgetting who I am now...

1111
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:11,890
♪ We will finally reunite ♪

1112
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:08,510
Xia Xiaolan,

1113
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:10,880
Where are you?

1114
00:39:12,280 --> 00:39:13,150
And where am I?

1115
00:39:22,190 --> 00:39:23,800
Dear passengers,

1116
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:26,320
the flight from Hangcheng...

1117
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,360
We can still board the plane
if we get in there

1118
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,420
within 10 minutes.

1119
00:39:28,590 --> 00:39:30,250
Do you think Mr. Mao will come?

1120
00:39:31,030 --> 00:39:32,160
He definitely will.

1121
00:39:32,430 --> 00:39:33,670
Mr. Mao is full of

1122
00:39:33,670 --> 00:39:34,960
ideals and ambitions.

1123
00:39:35,630 --> 00:39:37,030
If he really didn't care,

1124
00:39:37,070 --> 00:39:38,920
he wouldn't have taken on
the Haihua Hotel project.

1125
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:40,000
Didn't you come to Hangcheng

1126
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:41,200
for this very reason?

1127
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:43,190
You do know me well.

1128
00:39:43,630 --> 00:39:45,960
But he still hasn't shown up
at this point.

1129
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:48,090
Do you think he's stalling on purpose,

1130
00:39:49,630 --> 00:39:50,440
or...

1131
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:53,880
Oh, right.

1132
00:39:54,230 --> 00:39:55,070
Mr. Mao hasn't made a trip

1133
00:39:55,070 --> 00:39:56,190
out of Hangcheng for so long.

1134
00:39:56,190 --> 00:39:57,150
Could he be...

1135
00:40:01,630 --> 00:40:02,360
Mr. Mao!

1136
00:40:03,030 --> 00:40:03,820
Let me carry it.

1137
00:40:03,820 --> 00:40:04,280
I...

1138
00:40:04,760 --> 00:40:05,360
It's okay.

1139
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:05,760
Let me get it.

1140
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:07,280
Why so many procedures

1141
00:40:07,280 --> 00:40:08,480
on the way to the airport?

1142
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,280
What a hassle.

1143
00:40:09,960 --> 00:40:11,440
I should've been more considerate

1144
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:12,970
and picked you up from home.

1145
00:40:13,390 --> 00:40:14,980
Dear passengers,

1146
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:17,510
the flight from Hangcheng

1147
00:40:17,510 --> 00:40:18,590
to Shengcheng...

1148
00:40:18,670 --> 00:40:19,510
Let's go then.

1149
00:40:19,830 --> 00:40:20,360
Let's go.

1150
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,840
I'll just go take a look.

1151
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,030
Yes, sure.

1152
00:40:23,230 --> 00:40:23,890
Just a look.

1153
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:25,480
Please take your personal belongings.

1154
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,070
That is

1155
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:27,110
all we need.

1156
00:40:29,540 --> 00:40:33,590
[Shengcheng]

1157
00:40:35,760 --> 00:40:36,890
We should've driven

1158
00:40:37,150 --> 00:40:39,070
Zhou Cheng to the law firm
from the airport.

1159
00:40:39,070 --> 00:40:40,590
It wouldn't have been much of a detour.

1160
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:41,320
Mr. Mao

1161
00:40:41,320 --> 00:40:42,510
must be tired

1162
00:40:42,530 --> 00:40:43,550
after that three-hour flight.

1163
00:40:43,550 --> 00:40:45,710
It's better to go straight to the hotel.

1164
00:40:45,710 --> 00:40:47,360
After this road was completed,

1165
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:48,760
it's much faster to go from the airport

1166
00:40:48,760 --> 00:40:49,630
to downtown.

1167
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:50,840
Yes.

1168
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:52,630
Shengcheng develops quickly.

1169
00:40:52,630 --> 00:40:53,630
It only took six months

1170
00:40:53,630 --> 00:40:54,630
for this road to be made

1171
00:40:54,630 --> 00:40:56,490
and many buildings to take shape.

1172
00:41:14,630 --> 00:41:18,000
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

1173
00:41:18,020 --> 00:41:21,460
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

1174
00:41:21,640 --> 00:41:24,550
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

1175
00:41:25,020 --> 00:41:28,180
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

1176
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:34,070
♪ That'd be enough ♪

1177
00:41:33,590 --> 00:41:33,960
Thank you.

1178
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:34,550
Mr. Mao,

1179
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:35,960
how do you like it here?

1180
00:41:36,150 --> 00:41:36,880
Pretty nice.

1181
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:38,460
Ms. Xia,

1182
00:41:38,760 --> 00:41:39,360
it's done.

1183
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:40,880
Mr. Mao,

1184
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:42,010
get some rest today.

1185
00:41:42,110 --> 00:41:43,840
I'll show you around tomorrow.

1186
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:45,410
I don't want to wait.

1187
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:46,760
I'd like to visit your company

1188
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:48,490
after dropping off my luggage.

1189
00:41:49,590 --> 00:41:50,030
Okay.

1190
00:41:52,960 --> 00:41:53,920
I'm back!

1191
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:55,780
Cheng!

1192
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:58,760
A Hangcheng specialty, Dingsheng cake.

1193
00:41:58,760 --> 00:41:59,110
Chen,

1194
00:41:59,210 --> 00:42:00,110
split it with everyone.

1195
00:42:00,110 --> 00:42:01,170
Thanks. Good work.

1196
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:02,900
Come on.

1197
00:42:03,110 --> 00:42:03,910
Time to share.

1198
00:42:04,630 --> 00:42:05,000
Dong.

1199
00:42:05,440 --> 00:42:06,040
Thank you.

1200
00:42:06,070 --> 00:42:07,590
How is Hao's mood today?

1201
00:42:07,630 --> 00:42:08,630
Hao won a case.

1202
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:09,440
He said

1203
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:11,360
he'd treat us all to a meal
some other day.

1204
00:42:11,360 --> 00:42:12,880
If you have a favor to ask him for,
do it now.

1205
00:42:12,880 --> 00:42:14,010
He'll surely say yes.

1206
00:42:14,010 --> 00:42:14,970
Okay, got it.

1207
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:15,590
Alright.

1208
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:16,700
I'll have this.

1209
00:42:18,440 --> 00:42:18,900
Thanks.

1210
00:42:18,920 --> 00:42:19,550
Nice.

1211
00:42:19,630 --> 00:42:20,230
It's good.

1212
00:42:22,030 --> 00:42:22,490
Come in!

1213
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:23,650
Senior.

1214
00:42:25,960 --> 00:42:27,280
Here's a Hangcheng specialty,

1215
00:42:27,280 --> 00:42:28,210
Dingsheng cake.

1216
00:42:29,590 --> 00:42:31,120
You came for a talk, knowing

1217
00:42:31,150 --> 00:42:32,150
I'm in a good mood?

1218
00:42:33,360 --> 00:42:34,220
Check this out.

1219
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:36,920
What is it?

1220
00:42:37,550 --> 00:42:38,280
Just read it.

1221
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:44,350
[Investigation Report]
[The missing worker, Wang Qiang]

1222
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:46,070
He's that missing worker?
